  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Archmaester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ae/Archmaester.svg/50px-Archmaester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ae/Archmaester.svg/75px-Archmaester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ae/Archmaester.svg/100px-Archmaester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Archmaester</span><br />Glaive</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Archmaester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ae/Archmaester.svg/50px-Archmaester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ae/Archmaester.svg/75px-Archmaester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ae/Archmaester.svg/100px-Archmaester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Archmaester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Archmaester\">Archmaester</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">The Citadel</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlander\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Stormlander\">Stormlander</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Archmaester <b>Glaive</b> was an <a href=\"/index.php/Maesters#Archmaester\" title=\"Maesters\">archmaester</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a> born in the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>. He proposed that the \"King of a Thousand Years\", <a href=\"/index.php/Durran_Godsgrief\" title=\"Durran Godsgrief\">Durran Godsgrief</a>, was actually a succession of <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">monarchs</a> all bearing the same <a href=\"/index.php/Durran_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Durran (disambiguation)\">name</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_house_durrandon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_house_durrandon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Glaive&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_house_durrandon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_house_durrandon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Stormlands: House Durrandon.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404054318\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.063 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.238 